The China Media Group's Spring Festival Gala has been recognized by Guinness World Records as the world's most watched TV program since its debut in 1983. The gala for the upcoming Year of the Tiger will feature singing, dancing, comic sketches, opera, folk arts and tiger elements fused with harmony and reunion as the main themes. Dive into a world of modern Chinese culture and tradition and witness the creative spirit of China. Follow CGTN to the backstage of the gala and have a chat with the celebrities.